'''異黃酮'''（Isoflavones）是自然界的[[異黃酮類|異黃酮類]]化合物<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Kaufman PB, Duke JA, Brielmann H, Boik J, Hoyt JE |title=A comparative survey of leguminous plants as sources of the isoflavones, genistein and daidzein: implications for human nutrition and health |journal=J Altern Complement Med |volume=3 |issue=1 |pages=7–12 |year=1997 |pmid=9395689 |doi=10.1089/acm.1997.3.7 |citeseerx=10.1.1.320.9747 }}</ref>，其中許多是[[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]]的{{le|植物性雌激素|phytoestrogen}}<ref name="Heber, D 2008 176–181">{{cite book |author=Heber, D |title=Handbook of Nutrition and Food, Second Edition |editor=Berdanier, C.D |editor2=Dwyer, J.T. |editor3=Feldman, E.B. |pages=176–181 |publisher=CRC Press |year=2008 |isbn=978-0-8493-9218-4|doi=10.1201/9781420008890.ch70|chapter=Plant Foods and PhyTOChemicals in Human Health }}</ref>。異黃酮主要是由[[豆科|豆科]]植物所分泌。

異黃酮和許多相關的植物性雌激素會作為[[營養補充品|營養補充品]]販售，不過有關長期服用的安全性以及其健康上的助益，相關的科學證據非常的少<ref name="lpi">{{cite web|url=http://lpi.oregonstate.edu/mic/dietary-factors/phytochemicals/soy-isoflavones|title=Soy isoflavones|publisher=Micronutrient Information Center, Linus Pauling Institute, Oregon State University, Corvallis|date=2016|accessdate=27 July 2016|archive-date=2019-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191020134813/https://lpi.oregonstate.edu/mic/dietary-factors/phytochemicals/soy-isoflavones|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。有些研究指出服用高劑量異黃酮的潛在風險（例如對於[[乳癌|乳癌]]病史的女性），不過還沒有高品質的[[臨床研究|臨床研究]]可以證實其風險<ref name=lpi/>。

